  "method": [
    "Boil the chicken stock and the oregano in a large skillet once half a",
    "cup of liquid is left in the dish, about three minutes.",
    "Mix in the cubes of chicken, protect and withdraw the pan from the",
    "flame.",
    "In the cooking liquid, let the meat heat until just cooked, about eight",
    "minutes.",
    "Heat the ziti until cooked, about 13 minutes, in a big pot of hot, salted",
    "liquid.",
    "Flush and mix the pasta with the meat, feta, lime juice, pepper, salt,",
    "and coriander mixture.",
    "Stir until you have fully melted the cheese. Drop the cherry tomatoes",
    "Mix and serve hot."
